<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Post Notification - Merry Christmas!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #d32f2f; /* Festive red */
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .post-details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .post-details h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 2px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ„ New Post Alert! ðŸŽ„</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello, {{user_name}}!</h2>
            <p>Il y a un nouveau post sur le forum... Va donc y jeter un oeil:</p>
            <div class="post-details">
                <h3>{{post_title}}</h3>
                <p>{{post_description}}</p>
                <p><strong>By:</strong> {{post_author}}</p>
            </div>
            <p>Check it out and join the discussion! Click the link below:</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{post_link}}" style="color: #d32f2f; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">View the Post ðŸŽ…</a>
            </p>
            <p>Happy holidays, and thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>You're receiving this email because you're a valued member of our forum. ðŸŽ„</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
